      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "I am incredibly grateful for the experience my mother had at Mintygreen Care Suites. The environment is fantastic—it feels much more like a hotel than a traditional care facility, which meant we didn’t have to worry about sharing bathrooms with large groups of people.\n\nWhat truly sets them apart is their exceptional care and responsiveness. A huge, special thanks to Jojo and the friendly caretaking team. They conduct nighttime vital sign monitoring, which was a lifesaver. Because of this routine check, they quickly discovered that my mother’s SpO2 (oxygen) levels had dropped. The team responded immediately and was fully equipped with an oxygen concentrator to stabilize her without any delay.\n\nThe food arrangement is also excellent. They provide four meals a day, overseen by an in-house nutritionist to ensure everything is well-balanced. Furthermore, they are highly accommodating; they allowed us to bring in our own additional food and fruits, and even blended them for us so we could feed her easily. Highly recommended for any family looking for peace of mind and professional, compassionate care!",
      "textTranslated": null,
      "publishAt": "5 days ago",
      "publishedAtDate": "2026-05-03T05:12:22.571Z",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "reviewId": "Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kWmFVTnNNMWwyV0VoMU9XOXhUbUUxYldKdlNIYxAB",
